    "code": "import flopscope as fnp\n\nfnp.histogram([1, 2, 1], bins=[0, 1, 2, 3])\n\nfnp.histogram(fnp.arange(4), bins=fnp.arange(5), density=True)\n\nfnp.histogram([[1, 2, 1], [1, 0, 1]], bins=[0,1,2,3])\n\na = fnp.arange(5)\n\nhist, bin_edges = fnp.histogram(a, density=True)\n\nhist\n\nhist.sum()\n\nfnp.sum(hist * fnp.diff(bin_edges))",
